# UD Old English Cairo

Language: [Old English](/ang/index.html) (code: `ang`)<br/>
Family: IE

This treebank has been part of Universal Dependencies since the UD v2.16 release.

The following people have contributed to making this treebank part of UD: Lauren Levine, Junghyun Min, Amir Zeldes.

Repository: [UD_Old_English-Cairo](https://github.com/UniversalDependencies/UD_Old_English-Cairo)<br />

## Description

Old English [Cairo](https://github.com/UniversalDependencies/cairo) sentences with UD and additional annotations




Old English [Cairo](https://github.com/UniversalDependencies/cairo) sentences with UD and additional annotations
relevant to its historicity like hyperlemma, Indo-European root, and gloss.
